videos.description: South Carolina's PJ Dozier loses a shoe and Mississippi State's Xavian Stapleton lays it in.
videos.headline: Dozier loses a shoe and Mississippi State capitalizes

videos.description: South Carolina's Sindarius Thornwell and Mississippi State's Lamar Peters each knock down 3-pointers.
videos.headline: Mississippi State and South Carolina trade 3s

videos.description: Mississippi State's Tyson Carter nails a 3-pointer to help extend the Bulldogs's lead before halftime.
videos.headline: Mississippi State drains a 3 to pad lead

videos.description: South Carolina's Justin McKie drains the 3-pointer off the feed from Sindarius Thornwell as time expires in the half.
videos.headline: SC ties it at the buzzer going to halftime

videos.description: South Carolina's bad pass goes out of bounds and is caught in the megaphone of a Gamecocks' cheerleader.
videos.headline: Bad pass finds its way into cheerleader's megaphone

videos.description: Mississippi State's Xavian Stapleton comes out of nowhere to make the strong dunk off the missed shot.
videos.headline: Stapleton with the monster putback dunk

videos.description: Mississippi State's Mario Kegler makes the contested shot and draws the foul.
videos.headline: Kegler makes difficult floater

videos.description: Beth Mowins and Dalen Cuff break down South Carolina's Sindarius Thornwell's 28-point game against Mississippi State.
videos.headline: Breaking down Thornwell's big scoring game
